data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful townhome in Brunswick Plantation!  This end unit offers an open floor plan with high cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors and a sunny Carolina room overlooking a pond.  The upgraded kitchen has seating for 4 at the counter height bar, granite tops, stainless steel appliances and a large corner pantry.  The master suite is on the main level with a large updated bathroom and walk-in closet.  There are pocket doors in the master bathroom and the laundry room.  The upstairs has two large bedrooms and a large guest bath with 2 walk-in closets which provide plenty of storage.  Owners at the Smithfield townhomes have access to all of the amenities of Brunswick Plantation which include the Brunswick House indoor/outdoor pool, gym and event spaces.  Brunswick Plantation is a gated golf community with a staffed security house at the entrance.  There is a beautiful plantation style clubhouse, bar, restaurant and three 9-hole golf courses. Owners are able to drive their personal golf carts on the courses. The HOA fees also cover the cost of the master insurance policy, landscaping/exterior maintenance, pest treatment and trash pickup.  It is located just 20 minutes to the beach and is close to the airports and attractions in Myrtle Beach and Wilmington.
